Subject: Re: [T2] tight front end

At 06:44 AM 5/29/2002, Greg Thompson wrote:
>I'm at a loss as to what's causing the front end on my 74 SC to be 
>tight.  All ball joints have been replaced, new drag link, new tie rods, 
>re-bushed relay lever, steering box adjusted....

They probably don't know how to adjust the steering box.  It will be 
tighter at the center than at the locks.  If the box is adjusted snug when 
the wheel is off-center, it will be tight when on-center.  Tell them to 
loosen it up a bit.

-David

